{"word":"H5439 - סָבִיב - çâbîyb - saw-beeb' - About","slug":"H5439","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">סָבִיב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>çâbîyb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>saw-beeb'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>About"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E1;&#x05D1;&#x05D9;&#x05D1;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E1;&#x05D1;&#x05D9;&#x05D1; - sa&#x0302;b&#x0131;&#x0302;yb  seb&#x0131;&#x0302;yba&#x0302;h</b> - <i>saw-beeb', seb-ee-baw'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5437\">H5437</a>; (as noun) a <i>circle</i>, <i>neighbor</i>, or <i>environs</i>; but chiefly (as adverb, with or without preposition) <i>around: - </i>(place, round) about, circuit, compass, on every side."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4036\">H4036</a>, <a href=\"#/H4141\">H4141</a>, <a href=\"#/H4142\">H4142</a>, <a href=\"#/H4524\">H4524</a>, <a href=\"#/H5252\">H5252</a>, <a href=\"#/H5437\">H5437</a>, <a href=\"#/H5438\">H5438</a>"}]}